{"tid":1528923,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"提醒大家 敵人係不斷地進步 唔好再以為相同招數可以隨意重覆使用","createTime":"2019-09-01T15:34:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T14:28:11.000Z","uid":30791,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e28d52eaec341379c2430fbd03ed5488c7c1d57a","tid":1528923,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:34:11.000Z","msg":"今日機場已經係一例<br />\n上次塞完機場 今次敵人識得封巴士站 封地鐵 唔比大家走<br />\n今次大家整爛地鐵站設施 下次黨鐵必然會加以防備<br />\n大家必須時刻提高警覺 攻其無備 出其不意<br />\n不要大安旨意 墮入陷阱"},{"pid":"8326e1311f7d0879060f73384a931a0d1d1083e3","tid":1528923,"uid":153722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:36:36.000Z","msg":"係 同意<br />\n<br />\n機場咁重要<br />\n你入過一次佢地一定會度好晒abcde plan <br />\n<br />\n個人要be water玩進化<br />\n唔好之前做過咩都翻做"},{"pid":"29b53ab07f58f0b28cfce8b40236166fbea8bac3","tid":1528923,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:36:58.000Z","msg":"兵法 三十六計 你識幾多?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dLLcaS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dLLcaS</a>"},{"pid":"8d16ba84d2a33ed11664126b31277317c7ba8eed","tid":1528923,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:42:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aef0c3b156eedd798e3fffa3b164516b567047dc","tid":1528923,"uid":184379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:43:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2dd892b4a607e707d702ff70b060efdcb340b11","tid":1528923,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e9daf8f9dabb69db4003890c48e1134b5a0ea5a","tid":1528923,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:54:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3198ae2847891a1694ba6d7d0cb0da614183514","tid":1528923,"uid":275884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:55:34.000Z","msg":"香港人！我哋需要改變生活習慣救香港呀！<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dKJOcT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dKJOcT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0a23485081e7ba6bb7daef4f016e72e9cf9084be","tid":1528923,"uid":10201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:56:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ccd16a974f5f729f37a13d38fe430c51fcca682","tid":1528923,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:05:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37abbb7944cfb1abad42aad68184f63b184b898f","tid":1528923,"uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:11:35.000Z","msg":"係。之前中聯辦無防備，所以搞過中聯辦一次。<br />\n然之後匪共政府就整左大量防備畀中聯辦。以後都好難搞到中聯辦呢個賊巢了。"},{"pid":"20e755a556e8ca26f1ff67d06479b753a240e9e2","tid":1528923,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:13:05.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兵者，詭道也。故能而示之不能，用而示之不用，近而示之遠，遠而示之近。利而誘之，亂而取之，實而備之，強而避之，怒而撓之，卑而驕之，佚而勞之，親而離之，攻其不備，出其不意。此兵家之勝，不可先傳也。</span></strong></div>"},{"pid":"aa128c8697df072116ea08b37fb2b41bb4cef26a","tid":1528923,"uid":30791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:18:54.000Z","msg":"<strong>能而示之不能，用而示之不用</strong><br />\n隱藏真正的實力或者是讓不欲人知的訊息隱藏不露<br />\n<strong>近而示之遠，遠而示之近</strong><br />\n將主力或即將要發動的攻勢，佯裝到錯誤的距離及位置，令敵人評估失準<br />\n<strong>利而誘之</strong><br />\n用利益引誘貪利之人<br />\n<strong>亂而取之</strong><br />\n製造混亂，然後再乘虛而入<br />\n<strong>實而備之</strong><br />\n以充足的準備，去面對軍隊整齊有實力的對手<br />\n<strong>強而避之</strong><br />\n對強大士氣旺盛的敵人，先避其鋒，待其疲憊，再尋求反擊的機會<br />\n<strong>怒而撓之</strong><br />\n不斷騷擾敵人，令其破綻百出<br />\n<strong>卑而驕之</strong><br />\n以卑微的態度，令自大的對手失去危機感<br />\n<strong>佚而勞之</strong><br />\n以逸待勞，以最佳狀態迎接奔波疲勞的敵人<br />\n<strong>親而離之</strong><br />\n接近敵人的親信，然後進行離間行為，令其內外孤立<br />\n<strong>攻其不備</strong><br />\n攻擊對手無防備，或較薄弱的地方<br />\n<strong>出其不意</strong><br />\n在對手意想不到的地方及情勢下發動攻擊"},{"pid":"708b5f1192b92606d3e9e25e189c87ff52238209","tid":1528923,"uid":308916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:19:23.000Z","msg":"同意 同埋好多moon狗"},{"pid":"2842a3783be752f725b1567bda2af45f1ad54f89","tid":1528923,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:20:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb8ee1f331f7592d2e5148f5b9f875672a281ea","tid":1528923,"uid":51677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:27:17.000Z","msg":"光復青衣<br />\n如果機場係春袋<br />\n青衣就係輸精管<br />\n今次輸人數<br />\n但有遊行就可以儲齊多d人行動<br />\n而集會遊行正正係結集人既方法"},{"pid":"3c561b452f78ec3497914e279099aad5830a94f4","tid":1528923,"uid":47222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:27:37.000Z","msg":"機場907戰術：全部唔中途落車唔黑衫拖gip/扮接機 <br />\n到左就入返東涌再流水式入機場<br />\n如果必要情況下要set roadblock既set完即走做返市民<br />\n冇車走就商場shopping食飯唔洗心虛"},{"pid":"86ece89b8c8854998b8c0bb6ab005bc8f2486e95","tid":1528923,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afb8ee1f331f7592d2e5148f5b9f875672a281ea","tid":1528923,"uid":51677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:27:17.000Z","msg":"光復青衣<br />\n如果機場係春袋<br />\n青衣就係輸精管<br />\n今次輸人數<br />\n但有遊行就可以儲齊多d人行動<br />\n而集會遊行正正係結集人既方法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:31:43.000Z","msg":"其實人數無輸<br />\n<br />\n只係比交通加埋警犬散水撚控制到<br />\n<br />\n佢地好似人流管制咁不停叫人走<br />\n<br />\n入面係咁叫人走<br />\n<br />\n遲到果班就卡左係出面<br />\n<br />\n先谷唔起個人群"},{"pid":"37d143998c3a8179e3f399c6aac4b9d1d1771458","tid":1528923,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:43:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a191d89bfd6a04439ddf434db3462b785294a2","tid":1528923,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:28:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}